strategy:
They are very easy to kill, even for the most inexperienced Tibians. It may help to use the [[chase opponent]] button as they will always try to run away from you.

{{JSpoiler|You can use a [[Kitchen Knife]] or [[Obsidian Knife]] in its corpses during the [[Rottin Wood and the Married Men Quest]] and the daly task '''Lucky Charms''', in order to get 0-2 [[Rabbit's Foot]].
